{"tid":1429674,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"我正式宣佈，反港鐵不合作班連登仔根本同恐同組織冇分別","createTime":"2019-08-07T14:25:39.000Z","updateTime":"2019-08-07T16:48:43.000Z","uid":184458,"like":125,"dislike":162,"uniUserReply":68,"replies":[{"pid":"4b259b991fd59c967bd26a972e501240deca6ae5","tid":1429674,"uid":184458,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2019-08-07T14:25:39.000Z","msg":"琴日見到連登有post屌塞鐵個班手足，我身為每日都有發夢既前線我有野想講：<br />\n<br />\n1. 大家都只係為呢場運動好，所以先想搞咁多野。大家都係<span style=\"font-size: x-large;\"><span style=\"color: red;\">兄弟爬山用緊唔方法去打呢場仗</span></span>，有唔同意見都好<span style=\"font-size: x-large;\"><span style=\"color: red;\">絕對唔可以屌手足。</span></span>我見到啲留言話手足係鬼要起佢地底真係好心痛。<br />\n<br />\n2. 見到有人話兄弟爬山唔係咁用，直指不合作運動會影響成個香港形象同運動。連登喺唔比人用呢個方法爭取既同時，仲要否定埋人地爭取既方式。事實上805淨係塞鐵都<span style=\"font-size: x-large;\"><span style=\"color: orange;\">上哂外國新聞，就連旅遊警告都有提及地鐵不合作</span></span><br />\n<br />\n3. 我其實都係個谷入面，但係冇咩參與過討論。但係我呢幾日係入面見到既反對同屌佢地既言論真係好多。我認為你地真係要屌都唔需入去人地既行動谷屌手足，咁做會<span style=\"font-size: x-large;\"><span style=\"color: red;\">十分影響士氣。</span></span>兄弟爬山，不分化<br />\n<br />\n4. 其實叫佢地唔塞既原因好多都係因為民意，但係其實呢樣野真係冇理據證明到，始終要支持我地既就會繼續支持，好難突然調頭支持對家。話佢地係同溫層既同時，希望大家都要諗諗連登會唔會都係同溫層，始終<span style=\"font-size: x-large;\"><span style=\"color: red;\">好多風向都係由連登帶出黎，連登都有鬼㗎</span></span>，前幾日就有post屌前線手足<br />\n<br />\n5. 我見到佢地係有開投票，的確係有60%唔支持。但係呢個真係只係一個<span style=\"color: orange;\"><span style=\"font-size: large;\">百分比</span></span>，佢地睇左實際人數可能有唔岩。但係我想講好多野唔係一定要過半數先可以實行。如果全港公投唔過50％支持同性戀，咁係唔係所有人都應該反對同性戀<br />\n<br />\n大家兄弟爬山，為既都係同一個目標。我唔理你地係割唔割蓆都好，都<span style=\"font-size: x-large;\"><span style=\"color: orange;\">希望你地尊重返每個有係呢場運動付出，企出黎幫大家既香港人</span></span>，唔好一味唔同意就屌。我見到你地啲留言已經唔係叫佢地遲啲先搞，係「咪撚再搞」。<br />\n<br />\n記住，肯企出黎已經唔容易，肯帶頭搞不合作運動更少之又少，我相信佢地有管理得唔好既時候，但講到尾一個萬五人既谷的確係要好多時間同十分難去控制。我相信佢地有佢地既原因，希望大家唔好再屌手足。<br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"font-size: x-large;\"><strong><span style=\"color: red;\">不分化，不割蓆，不篤灰，不被捕，不受傷<br />\n<br />\n香港加油</span></strong></span>"},{"pid":"b4be098882937ddb9524ed99ac6766fdd4325ab3","tid":1429674,"uid":184458,"like":0,"dislike":4,"score":-4,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-07T14:26:44.000Z","msg":"自推"},{"pid":"c58faba153f7eb0ee20e4541db63163ebe5c54e3","tid":1429674,"uid":8482,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-07T14:27:24.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"a4b219fefe28ce509e444a9bf54372d675a64d0f","tid":1429674,"uid":184458,"like":1,"dislike":3,"score":-2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-07T14:28:18.000Z","msg":"再推"},{"pid":"c99d1ece78b0c34bcf671b3e4e2ea73228664561","tid":1429674,"uid":206811,"like":16,"dislike":3,"score":13,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-08-07T14:28:57.000Z","msg":"都覺得真係唔好再屌手足，<br />\n咁搞法邊有人仲肯出嚟做嘢"},{"pid":"c1c057ea3f4fae92fc86a9b2042d35f70214dcaf","tid":1429674,"uid":184458,"like":1,"dislike":2,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-07T14:32:43.000Z","msg":"光復香港，時代革命"},{"pid":"bb0bf29922c2e780317dc3caa6e6dd76eb5b069e","tid":1429674,"uid":264291,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-07T14:33:23.000Z","msg":"推。"},{"pid":"bbe05c8b54c29402ef07a5dc5d18ec737f867ee8","tid":1429674,"uid":184458,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-07T14:34:25.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"f3dfded3f9b237e12585f149000d05d99cda86b3","tid":1429674,"uid":184458,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-07T14:34:37.000Z","msg":"再泥"},{"pid":"008395891f232915efc409b81fbd45ba143bcf56","tid":1429674,"uid":184458,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-07T14:34:57.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"ebdecc13bb0db93eeece65515d09249004027a3c","tid":1429674,"uid":289081,"like":3,"dislike":2,"score":1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-08-07T14:35:42.000Z","msg":"支持！<br />\n不割𥱊，不篤灰，不指責！<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"2baa7a71a7d8fe23305a2d81aec00877ff22be3f","tid":1429674,"uid":184458,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-07T14:36:27.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"7dd83bc73152f5955399e145ed9a415913ce2efa","tid":1429674,"uid":184458,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-07T14:36:42.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"9d3d43b921cc72bddfda6cbb064533ca7d623a8c","tid":1429674,"uid":22360,"like":30,"dislike":0,"score":30,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-08-07T14:36:55.000Z","msg":"不割，但不支持近期再搞"},{"pid":"83b5ce2485227f06ae02ff80cc8c28910cf8088f","tid":1429674,"uid":184458,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-07T14:37:21.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"fd2c2a6199afd587223c9d5c285ca7ec3a386371","tid":1429674,"uid":184458,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-07T14:37:42.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"c1cc344fdeb4e93d863b18c08edb6c27535147c2","tid":1429674,"uid":287594,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-07T14:38:11.000Z","msg":"好文分享，我地需要呢種一眼就記得嘅文宣<br />\n<br />\n【文宣新方向】乜鬼野五大，七大訴求呀??<br />\n<a href=\"https://lih.kg/1429008\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lih.kg/1429008</a><br />\n- 分享自 LIHKG 討論區"},{"pid":"7a83b5b50df938541b6a275d47587d9cf66e492f","tid":1429674,"uid":233325,"like":18,"dislike":0,"score":18,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-07T14:38:19.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/itdog3.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n不割，但不支持近期再搞"},{"pid":"1bc72f835a2e8c4869e0c2a452303d1abc8b0660","tid":1429674,"uid":206811,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"quote":{"pid":"ebdecc13bb0db93eeece65515d09249004027a3c","tid":1429674,"uid":289081,"like":3,"dislike":2,"score":1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-08-07T14:35:42.000Z","msg":"支持！<br />\n不割𥱊，不篤灰，不指責！<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><