41a1f17b24d03ec478d36e70bb","tid":1429674,"uid":43724,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-07T15:39:42.000Z","msg":"<span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\">兄弟爬山  放核彈都唔割 </span></span>"},{"pid":"ee8447b70682b46b75bb69630f3fe3ceb7511670","tid":1429674,"uid":267881,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-07T15:39:53.000Z","msg":"唔堅持做一D脱離連些主流嘅事<br />\n<br />\n我仲以為呢個係共識添..."},{"pid":"e11c371aef32fdc224950b09da2c3544ffa16640","tid":1429674,"uid":226417,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-07T15:39:55.000Z","msg":"推呀"},{"pid":"7e7d4fe6306e5abf9706fe486aa54b37dc6afce7","tid":1429674,"uid":226417,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-07T15:40:20.000Z","msg":"push"},{"pid":"c33fe81ee2761e0a1df1addb9dc2e06c2f0723f9","tid":1429674,"uid":32800,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-07T15:40:37.000Z","msg":"我自己一定唔割<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/bye.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/bye.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/bye.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n連登嘅巴絲好明白不合作運動嘅目的同背景<br />\n但我地唔可能活係自己嘅象牙塔入面咁不理世事<br />\n<strong>中間民意係好重要</strong><br />\n的確不合作運動會令到班好想返工嘅港豬反感<br />\n我地要諗下點樣收佢地過黎<br />\n<br />\n班畜牲已經好幫手咁拉左好多屌走佢地嘅街坊<br />\n令佢地都覺得黑警濫權濫捕<br />\n班街坊代表左好多未覺醒嘅香港人<br />\n佢地未必接受到前線嘅衝擊場面同埋返唔到工<br />\n<br />\n前線手足係時候要諗一諗不停咁衝仲係咪有效<br />\n情況同出TG一樣<br />\n5年前雨革出TG已經好大迴響<br />\n到今日好似唔食過TG就冇出過去發夢一樣<br />\n呢d場面係會麻木架<br />\n再者好多人會好心痛你地去送頭比人打比人拉<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/wail.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/wail.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/wail.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n希望前線們諗下個方向啦<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/lihkg.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/lihkg.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/lihkg.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"a7f0e1b8c592687b0dfec8ed5d6d8f4a36eb473a","tid":1429674,"uid":226417,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-07T15:41:07.000Z","msg":"push"},{"pid":"7a5d8af60f1698c91de28ea2ba7d06e8f8b358fe","tid":1429674,"uid":226417,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-07T15:41:53.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"34cd1cc3bf7eec8ac09c0a713956fdaa033da8ec","tid":1429674,"uid":62785,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-07T15:42:09.000Z","msg":"拿<br />\n我識嘅外國人睇完當地報道85 地鐵事件後都係唔認同兼疑惑<br />\n有人問點解唔俾想坐車既人坐車<br />\n<br />\n我自己就覺得已經做得好好<br />\n因為香港基本上真係停運咗一整日<br />\n仲要無大反撲反對聲<br />\n表示咗強大民意基礎<br />\n<br />\n但短期內唔好再搞住了"},{"pid":"a82d73290d8b1e4ba4f10b69a23453612fa16baf","tid":1429674,"uid":226417,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-07T15:42:51.000Z","msg":"推比樓主知"},{"pid":"19ebfec0b5b7996c66a8531aa83c94fb85929ffe","tid":1429674,"uid":14706,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-07T15:43:08.000Z","msg":"借個位 唔好意思<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/RdZdASD.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FRdZdASD.png&h=813d89d3&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/OosKHxD.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FOosKHxD.jpg&h=a66cdf95&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/pcQHucD.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FpcQHucD.jpg&h=1fe4606e&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/GD8t9cD.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FGD8t9cD.jpg&h=0cffabdb&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"848b013b0e29e418b4e3713c7c31af268b96ad71","tid":1429674,"uid":226417,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-07T15:43:38.000Z","msg":"推上熱門"},{"pid":"a1b9ad3061f0a9478ae91e68652b7390d02a9d7c","tid":1429674,"uid":30503,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-07T15:43:53.000Z","msg":"不如開個帖投票啦，我本人就反對近期再塞鐵"},{"pid":"bcbdddde99e48630af232